comment: What this all comes down to is a very critical matter and the reason is, we have come as a nation to respect and admire the equality of woman across the nation and show support and protect them against the harm and wrongdoing of mistreatment towards them in one way or another. Whenever there is an accusation made on their behalf you almost always want to believe them and blame the male because you sympathize how wrong it must have been for them to go through that and also want to show your support in bringing justice to the matter, but in this case it was not so. This was a major step back in some ways more than others for an accusation for or against a woman especially in the Hollywood films business. Aside from this story that shed light on wrong accusations that can and still exist of the poorly accused men today is the only positive to this story, Amber Heard greatly charged a bad rep for females in the near future that may go through the same thing and will be harder to get their story across in a believable manner. People will always look back at similar cases and compare them, something to fall back on and say ‚Äúwell remember the case where Amber Heard lied and blamed her husband and faked bruises and soars‚Äù it loses all credibility at that point. Luckily for the men in this case that are being honest finally stand a fair chance.

  You were all taught NOT TO EVER EVER HIT A WOMAN NO MATTER WHAT SHE DID OR DOES! and coming forward might look not masculine but I promise you men out there: the good women. comment:
YOUTUBE channels, please report the Depp vs Heard accurately with the right words and discontinue repetition of the same material. Johnny needs this!!

I am a feminist and am strongly opposed to any kind of abuse, but can‚Äôt stand behind Heard on this one!

Clearly I see that Depp has been abused by a narcissist. Why has no Youtube channels pointed out that Heard is highly MANIPULATIVE in recordings and she has set him up for ENTRAPMENT by recording him for years.  

She undermines and gaslights him constantly, telling him he doesnt understand, and is the queen of word salad, dancing in circles, trying to put blame on him, while she is recording. Yet Depp is always patient, polite, doesnt take the bait, just is loving and wants peaceful closure.

She feeds him xanex while she is recording. She secretly videos him when she knows he will come home angry, repeatedly asking, ‚Äú you werent here this morning were you? ( probably at Elon Musks house and didnt take his calls) Totally set him up!!

She has had INFIDELITY with a couple guys while married to Depp. Elevator videos don‚Äôt lie.

It is also clear that she has abandonment issues, every time there was a confrontation Depp would leave, and that threw her into a anxiety and rage. Im sure all Heard‚Äôs exes knew about this experience with her.

To be fair, they had a toxic relationship (largely due to her insecurities) and the fact that they BOTH were drinking and using drugs more because they were both unhappy. They both need healing, she needs to heal her long-term abandonment issues and anger from her childhood. He needs to heal from recent narcissistic abuse, and question why he was a co-dependant for this type of person to begin with.

So Youtube channels, use the right words to define the scenerio, rather than repeating the same stuff over and over. Narcissist, Manipulative, Entrapment, Infidelity, Abandonment Issues, Addictions. These words will make a difference in court.

Johnny deserves better, and Im pretty sure he would agree with me on this!
